  "description": "Chicago in the 30s. You are an aspiring boss of a criminal organization and plan to make big money. Easier said than done, though - you will have to decide how much money to spend on money and how much to invest. And doing a good job might be bad for your health, since other organizations might hire hitmen to eliminate you.<br><br>The game features stylish graphics and is presented - not unlike <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=King+Of+Chicago\">King of Chicago</a> - through conversations with other goons of your mob. And if you lose all your money or men, you will get the unforgettable message by your right-hand man... &quot;What a schmuck you are, Mugsy.&quot;",
